                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050710-68-off387 t18050710-68-cd388"></join>, a pig, value 2 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050710-68-victim686" type="victimName">
