                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050710-68-defend684 t18050710-68-punish392"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
